{"code": 0, "data": [{"cid": 1717375, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 337829, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "为什么还有人选第一个或者第三个选项?", "timestamp": 1621854506, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1717389, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 337829, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "能搞到钱不？能？那就是好事", "timestamp": 1621854670, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1717397, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 337829, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "学术界内部造神不好；但是造一个学术界的神来给外界看，还是有可能有好处的。", "timestamp": 1621854740, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1717411, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 337829, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "量子通信警告", "timestamp": 1621854830, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1717412, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 337829, "reply_to": 1717375, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 为什么还有人选第二个选项?", "timestamp": 1621854842, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1717652, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Francis", "pid": 337829, "reply_to": 1717375, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 因为敏锐的定位到了dz在冲袁老", "timestamp": 1621856774, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1717663, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Francis", "pid": 337829, "reply_to": 1717375, "tag": null, "text": "造不造神且不说，看见dz这样自己不为国奉献还冲无私奉献祖国的人我就气", "timestamp": 1621856817, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1717706, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 337829, "reply_to": 1717663, "tag": null, "text": "Re Francis: 就是论事，不涉及袁老，单单看造神这件事", "timestamp": 1621857219, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1717755, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Francis", "pid": 337829, "reply_to": 1717706, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 单看这个其实有助于红色教育，可参照每次某清一演马兰花开就有一堆人哭的哗啦啦的", "timestamp": 1621857873, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1717764, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 337829, "reply_to": 1717755, "tag": null, "text": "Re Francis: 既然说了是造神，难免有夸大嫌疑，套用到红色教育，这不是洗脑吗", "timestamp": 1621857970, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1717765, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Francis", "pid": 337829, "reply_to": 1717755, "tag": null, "text": "Re Francis: 我觉得不只是学术界，政坛也是一样的，比如之前总书记来清华盛况，我们东亚人的慕强心理是这么多年封建传统残留下来的，也是对于大疆域多人口多民族国家治理必须的", "timestamp": 1621857977, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1717770, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Francis", "pid": 337829, "reply_to": 1717764, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 我觉得本质差不多吧，当时邓的贡献很突出，但也有别的人\n而我相信所做的贡献和被宣传的比例不是完全一致", "timestamp": 1621858051, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1717779, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Francis", "pid": 337829, "reply_to": 1717770, "tag": null, "text": "Re Francis: 而且也会产生一种偶像效应，例如祖国不会忘记，有助于年轻人投身宏大的爱国事业", "timestamp": 1621858121, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1717819, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 337829, "reply_to": 1717765, "tag": null, "text": "Re Francis: 那我们两个立场和价值观已经不同了，这个问题也就很难达成共识了", "timestamp": 1621858556, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1717823, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 337829, "reply_to": 1717779, "tag": null, "text": "Re Francis: 你是想控制民众，利用民众投身到国家建设，而我不是这么想的", "timestamp": 1621858594, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1717831, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Francis", "pid": 337829, "reply_to": 1717823, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 我是站在国家角度去尝试分析的，不代表我自己支持这种做法，自己来说，我只是很佩服袁老这样为粮食奉献了一生的无私的科学家", "timestamp": 1621858701, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1717836, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Francis", "pid": 337829, "reply_to": 1717831, "tag": null, "text": "Re Francis: 我觉得多造点这样的神总比娱乐圈造神或者官员造神好", "timestamp": 1621858743, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1717855, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 337829, "reply_to": 1717836, "tag": null, "text": "Re Francis: 我们不需要神", "timestamp": 1621858900, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1717858, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 337829, "reply_to": 1717831, "tag": null, "text": "Re Francis: 我也尊敬每一个在科研在建设领域深耕的人，但不意味着我希望有所谓的“神”出现", "timestamp": 1621858969, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1718198, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Grace", "pid": 337829, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "爱因斯坦算造神吗？", "timestamp": 1621862162, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1722219, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Hans", "pid": 337829, "reply_to": 1717397, "tag": null, "text": "Re Carol: +1", "timestamp": 1621926611, "type": "text", "url": ""}], "post": {"deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "likenum": 7, "pid": 337829, "reply": 21, "tag": null, "text": "学术界造神是件好事吗？", "timestamp": 1621854375, "type": "text", "updated_at": 1621926610, "url": "", "vote": {"vote_data": {"是": 32, "不是": 157, "看具体情况而定": 74, "吃瓜": 67}, "vote_options": ["是", "不是", "看具体情况而定", "吃瓜"]}}}